      <section eId="sec_71_2721">
        <num>71-2721</num>
        <heading>Enforcement of Article 27 and this title</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A fine, as set forth in subdivision two of this section;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Following a hearing in accordance with the procedures set forth in\nsection 71-2723 of this chapter, payment of the cost of legally\ndisposing of the hazardous waste unlawfully possessed and restoring to\nits original state the area where substances were released unlawfully in\nviolation of sections 27-0914, 71-2710, 71-2711, 71-2712, 71-2713 and\n71-2714 of this chapter;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Any other sentence authorized by law, including imprisonment; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Any combination of such fine, payment of the cost of disposal and\nrestoration, and any other sentence authorized by law, including\nimprisonment.\n  2. Fines. A sentence to pay a fine shall be a sentence to pay an\namount fixed by the court, not exceeding the higher of:\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Three hundred thousand dollars for a class C felony;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Two hundred twenty-five thousand dollars for a class D felony;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>One hundred fifty thousand dollars for a class E felony;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Thirty-seven thousand five hundred dollars for a class A\nmisdemeanor;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_e">
          <num>(e)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Fifteen thousand dollars for a class B misdemeanor; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2721__subsec_f">
          <num>(f)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Double the amount of the defendant's gain from the commission of\nthe crime.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
